contents.description: From the Emmy-winning Greg Daniels (The Office, Parks & Rec) comes a hilarious new sci-fi comedy. In the future people can upload their consciousness to a luxurious digital afterlife. When party boy Nathan gets uploaded to a virtual resort he meets the down-to-earth Nora who starts as his customer service “angel”, but becomes so much more as she helps him find friendship, love and purpose.
contents.title: Upload

contents.description: Uri guides six young tourists through the abandoned town where the families of the workers of Chernobyl nuclear plant use to live.
contents.title: Chernobyl Diaries

contents.description: A sci-fi anthology series with stand-alone episodes based on the works of Philip K. Dick.
contents.title: Philip K. Dick's Electric Dreams
Amy Winehouse Back To Black: Classic Albums
The End of the F***ing World

contents.description: O demônio de Natal está de volta e agora libera sua ira sobre os moradores de uma pequena cidade. Apenas uma jovem nada comum pode ser capaz de deter o Krampus. Ninguém está seguro!
contents.title: Krampus - O Acordo
David Bowie - Black Tie, White Noise

contents.description: O que acontece quando seis sortudos estranhos, três rapazes bonitos e três mulheres bonitas e sensuais de todo o mundo ganham um concurso aleatório - uma viagem com todas as despesas pagas para uma incrível casa de praia na glamorosa Malibu, Califórnia, graças a uma grande Empresa de Internet - apenas para descobrir que eles têm que compartilhá-lo uns com os outros.
contents.title: American Beach House (Portuguese audio)
Black Lives Matter - O Movimento Negro Hoje

contents.description: anet Slate (Julianne Michelle) tem 24 anos e decide se mudar para um pequeno apartamento na cidade, sem saber que não viverá sozinha. Aos poucos, começa a experimentar eventos sobrenaturais que a levarão até a morte.
contents.title: 1303 - Apartamento do Mal

contents.description: Film students break into an abandoned insane asylum to do paranormal research and quickly discover ghosts are real.
contents.title: Grave Encounters 2

contents.description: Combining romance, drama, fantasy and mystery, Benjamin Button chronicles an odd romance that sparks between a 30-year-old woman (Academy Award winner Cate Blanchett - The Aviator) and a man (Brad Pitt - Troy) who, at 50, begins aging backwards.
contents.title: The Curious Case of Benjamin Button
Vitória: A Vida de uma Rainha

contents.description: Épico biográfico do controverso e influente líder nacionalista negro, desde o início de sua carreira e carreira de gângster, até seu ministério como membro da Nação do Islã.
contents.title: Malcolm X

contents.description: A dark force threatens Alpha, a vast metropolis and home to species from a thousand planets. Special operatives Valerian and Laureline must race to identify the marauding menace.[Showcase Channel]
contents.title: Valerian & the City of a Thousand Planets

contents.description: Freshman Charlie is a loner until he falls under the spell of the free-spirited Sam and her fearless stepbrother, Patrick, in this adaptation of Stephen Chbosky's best-selling novel.
contents.title: The Perks of Being a Wallflower
Jurassic World - A Fuga do Indominous Rex

contents.description: After being locked behind sacred glass in the Warren's artifacts room, Annabelle awakens the evil spirits in the room, who set their sights on the Warrens’ daughter and her friends.
contents.title: Annabelle Comes Home

contents.description: In this comedy, Kirk, an average guy, can’t believe his luck when the successful and gorgeous babe Molly falls for him. His smart-ass friends, his crazy family, and even his obnoxious ex-girlfriend are just as shocked as he is.
contents.title: She's Out of My League

contents.description: Uma morte ocorre acidentalmente no ringue e Boyka passa a questionar tudo aquilo em que acredita. Ao descobrir que a mulher do homem morto está em apuros, Bokya faz de tudo para ajudá-la.
contents.title: Boyka: O Imbatível

contents.description: A workaholic woman gets out of the office late on Christmas Eve - what a time to discover that the parking garage attendant is a psycho who's got every escape route covered! A superior, violent thriller!
contents.title: P2

contents.description: A recently released ex-con and his adopted younger brother are forced to go on the run. Chased by a vengeful criminal, the feds and a cadre of otherworldly soldiers, their only protection is a found weapon of mysterious ancestry.
contents.title: KIN

contents.description: A tough detective (Denzel Washington) matches wits with a cunning bank robber (Clive Owen), as a tense hostage crisis is unfolding. Into the volatile situation comes a woman named Madaline (Jodie Foster), a mysterious power broker who has a hidden agenda and threatens to push a tense situation past the breaking point.
contents.title: Inside Man

contents.description: An alcoholic surgeon loses a patient on his operating table abd tries to expiate his guilt by forming a relation with the deceased's son.
contents.title: The Killing of a Sacred Deer
